                            <comment id="81644" author="adilger" created="Tue, 15 Apr 2014 17:49:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The selection of the shared space is handled by the test environment using the SHARED_DIRECTORY environment variable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
